---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Hotel Iubit" description="Read our privacy policy to understand how we protect and use your personal information.">
  <div class="bg-dark text-white py-16 text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl prose prose-lg prose-primary">
      <p>Last updated: July 23, 2026</p>
      
      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>Welcome to Hotel Iubit. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you interact with us or book a stay at our hotel.</p>
      
      <h2>2. Our Services</h2>
      <p>We operate as a standard lodging hotel. Our primary service is providing room accommodations. Reservations can be made through our website, in person at our front desk, or via phone call. Please note that all meal services are separate and incur extra charges.</p>
      
      <h2>3. Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>To process your room booking and provide our services, we collect necessary personal information, including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Identity Data:</strong> Your first name, last name, and proof of identity (as required at check-in).</li>
        <li><strong>Contact Data:</strong> Your email address, phone number, and billing/home address.</li>
        <li><strong>Financial Data:</strong> Payment details such as credit card information used for securing and paying for your room reservation and any extra meal charges.</li>
        <li><strong>Reservation Data:</strong> Arrival and departure dates, room preferences, and special requests.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>4. How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <p>We only use your personal data for practical, business-related purposes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>To process and confirm your room booking (whether online, by phone, or in person).</li>
        <li>To process payments for your room and any additional charges, such as meals.</li>
        <li>To communicate with you regarding your reservation.</li>
        <li>To comply with legal and regulatory obligations for guest registration.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We employ standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, accidental loss, or disclosure. We prioritize keeping your booking and payment details safe.</p>
      
      <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy or your personal data, please contact us directly at our front desk, by phone, or via email.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
